div.div: OK after having the same problem I've found the solution. In your .spec file edit the hiddenimport to add the following: hiddenimport=[ #all your previous hidden imports (2 more lines were trimmed) If you still have an error message (like me) related to scipy this time add the following: hiddenimport=[ #all your previous hidden imports (3 more lines were trimmed) Hopefully your script should be good to go! source of the scipy fix: here
